name: Vicky Singh
summary: Full Stack Developer with 3+ years of experience in building scalable web applications using .NET and Angular. Strong in backend development, database design, and delivering clean, maintainable code. Passionate about learning new technologies and solving real-world problems.

experiance.description: Worked as a full stack developer developing enterprise web applications using ASP.NET Core, Angular, and SQL Server. Collaborated with cross-functional teams to design APIs, implement UI features, and improve application performance.
Developed backend services using .NET Core and Entity Framework Core. Integrated Kafka for event-driven communication and contributed to code reviews and system design discussions.
